<div class="text-justify mt-5">
    <p class="lead">We build this website as part of a collaborative work between the CNAM and Ingemedia, respectively an IT engineering school and an audio-visual communication school, with the aim of promoting toursim in the Hiroshima region in Japan.</p>
    <p class="lead">The timeline describes the main periods of the Hiroshima region, and the interactive map presents some monuments of the Saigoku road.</p>
